name: Jump Frog
description:
Game Jam Theme: Frogs

Game Jam Limitation: Only one level

This is a platformer game created for the Mini Jam 79. You click with the mouse to jump with the frog and the goal is to reach the top of this one level.

Tilemap Art: Nature pixel art

Music: Ukulele by https://www.bensound.com/

Sound: dustyroom.com

Created: 2nd of May for the Mini Jam 79: Frogs
